{"tid":2028442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港好地地 搞咩國安法，國際實制裁香港，經濟實玩完，分分鐘打仗！","createTime":"2020-05-21T22:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T02:53:32.000Z","uid":244332,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5b17abb44ed84c13b46e21f839db433e6c961ba1","tid":2028442,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T22:33:49.000Z","msg":"到時股票跌<br />\n樓價跌<br />\n打爛工人飯碗，手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港好地地，唔好阻我收成期<br />\n分分鐘<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打仗</span></span>添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要團結港豬 反國安法，<br />\n根本要用呢招，<br />\n講民主自由佢睬你都傻</span></span>"},{"pid":"e2d720d40d1e9ea66151cfb41f230dbad733f583","tid":2028442,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:52:50.000Z","msg":"我地要同共產黨對賭香港對世界經濟嘅影響力<br />\n賭美國守香港嘅決心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來佢地日日扮一國兩制<br />\n搞個假法治搵黑警濫捕<br />\n搵紅官亂判<br />\n班鬼佬都無乜位入香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而家支共直接插旗撕破埋假面具<br />\n今次係我地香港人最後生機<br />\n成件串埋港共 黑警 紅官 賣港狗（開始有狗話佢地只係奉命行事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奉命賣港殺人？）<br />\n<br />\n共產黨以一國一制搞亂香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時外國想淨係制裁班共狗又好<br />\n成個香港制裁都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地都無得輸<br />\n因為無野差得過跟住落嚟落入支那手<br />\n變新疆2.0"},{"pid":"094f93076850985fb3d45a8a4267a657adfa0dda","tid":2028442,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:28:39.000Z","msg":"依個方向文宣幾好"},{"pid":"8c17fadacb38e90d402c88befbe9561335b37576","tid":2028442,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"094f93076850985fb3d45a8a4267a657adfa0dda","tid":2028442,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:28:39.000Z","msg":"依個方向文宣幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48fb0e9d3c6d95cdd7c35ad8a78eddf0385fb41","tid":2028442,"uid":179144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對国安法 阻我收成期</span></span>"},{"pid":"6744fdbdf300a93579338b77d961369df0a07a42","tid":2028442,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"中共立法打殘香港經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1746dda0be7545130e2b6e6dd9f8c2db242c791d","tid":2028442,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c48fb0e9d3c6d95cdd7c35ad8a78eddf0385fb41","tid":2028442,"uid":179144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對国安法 阻我收成期</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:31:08.000Z","msg":"啱，咪撚阻我收成期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92f74f8efd0f8c98363d1c093298e17cc52818c","tid":2028442,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b17abb44ed84c13b46e21f839db433e6c961ba1","tid":2028442,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T22:33:49.000Z","msg":"到時股票跌<br />\n樓價跌<br />\n打爛工人飯碗，手停口停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港好地地，唔好阻我收成期<br />\n分分鐘<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打仗</span></span>添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要團結港豬 反國安法，<br />\n根本要用呢招，<br />\n講民主自由佢睬你都傻</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T02:41:40.000Z","msg":"攬炒派無視警暴 反屈市民"},{"pid":"0d26f55ca0a922dbd8b8f1c07dc5012f3d41e11f","tid":2028442,"uid":273218,"like":0,